defaultthe right training, actually has a platform on which it can be built.  There is a time for that to be developed.  Certainly in dealings with the 
defaultNational Malaria Control 
defaultboard and so on, they are very enthusiastic to find ways to grow and to get better at the task that they have in front of them, and they are being given the liberty to do it now, which they have not had until recently.  The right kind of investment in capacity building through the system is going to be important, but not rushed.
