defaultGreg Powerdefault: I should start by declaring a conflict of interest in that, although we work very closely with the Westminster Foundation, we are also sometimes competing with them for work.  There is certainly merit in that idea of building up that brand.  The 
defaultWestminster
default brand is incredibly strong.  We have experienced this because
